  "notes": "This recording is also known under the name: \r\n\"Masada 4\".\r\nRecorded at RPM, New York City on February 20, 1994.\r\nMastered at Foothill Digital, NYC.\r\n\r\nThe original pressing of this record was never available for retail, it was given away by DIW in exchange of the proof of buying the three first Masada, in June 1995.\r\nThe record was reissued in 1997 as a regular record.\r\n\r\nⒸⓅ 1995 diskUnion\r\nJASRAC R-9680307\r\n",
